ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely attend this course - two phenomenal researchers explain deep insides they gained in decades of research in a very comprehensive manner in order to instruct you about means that actually work and ignite development/growth (and warn about empty promises that do not promote development). Also improves your understanding of empirics and methodology.
overview of topics and methodologies. good lecture. introduction to datasets and literature.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It informed me to a great deal which field to choose for further research.
